      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and runs like a dream! This is the perfect find for someone who wants a dependable car that looks great without the 'brand new' price tag. It's got plenty of life left in it and is totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
